							<span class="text-gray-500">â†’ 85% confidence</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Instant Funding</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">One-click payments through Stripe or GitHub Sponsors. No accounts, no friction, just value exchange.</p>
						<div class="code-block">
							<span class="text-green-400">$</span> <span class="text-gray-300">/fund 500</span><br />
							<span class="text-gray-500">â†’ Payment link ready</span><br />
							<span class="text-gray-500">â†’ Click to fund</span><br />
							<span class="text-gray-500">â†’ Work starts now!</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="feature-card">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
							<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Autonomous Execution</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">AI agents can implement, test, and submit PRs automatically. You review, we deliver.</p>
						<div class="code-block">
							<span class="text-green-400">ðŸ¤–</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Agent starting...</span><br />
